    "name": "Explore With Me - Comments Feature",
    "description": "**Comments feature.**  \n  \nThe collection creates all required entities automatically (User → Category → Event), publishes the event, verifies that comments cannot be created for unpublished events, then tests all CRUD operations for comments.EndFragment \n  \n**Before running:** \n1. Start Explore With Me application.\n2. Make sure server is available at http://localhost:8080.\n3. Run the whole collection.",
